<section>
    <h2>🎓 Diverse Academic Programs in Georgia</h2>
    <p>Georgia offers top-tier undergraduate and postgraduate programs like BBA, MBA, Computer Science, Pharmacy, Economics, and Public Health, following the Bologna Process.</p>

    <h3>📊 Master of Business Administration (MBA)</h3>
    <p>Duration: 2 years | Language: English | Eligibility: Bachelor’s + English proficiency</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Careers: Management, consulting, entrepreneurship, finance, HR</li>
        <li>Global Scope: UK, Canada, USA, Europe, UAE, Singapore</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>💻 Computer Science & IT</h3>
    <p>Duration: Bachelor’s 4 years, Master’s 2 years | Language: English</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Careers: Developer, Data Analyst, Cybersecurity, AI/ML, Cloud</li>
        <li>Work Abroad: Germany (Blue Card), Canada (Tech Pilot), UK, Netherlands, UAE</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>💊 Pharmacy</h3>
    <p>Duration: Bachelor’s 4 years, Master’s 2 years | Language: English</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Careers: Clinical Pharmacist, R&D, Sales & Marketing, Regulatory Affairs</li>
